〈'''惡夜魔境'''〉（{{lang-en|''It Came from the Nightosphere''}}）是《[[探險活寶|探險活寶]]》[[探險活寶_(第二季)|第二季]]的第1集。在[[卡通頻道|卡通頻道]]2010年10月11日播出。本集以[[阿寶·馬頓斯|阿寶]]和魔法狗[[酷狗老皮|老皮]]為主角，講述艾薇爾唱出跟她和疏遠父親之間有關的一首歌後，阿寶釋放惡夜魔境的首領——[[探險活寶人物表|韓森]]，亦為[[瑪瑟琳·阿巴迪爾|艾薇爾]]的父親。然而，勉強協助被激怒的艾薇爾的阿寶，阻止他吸取所有哇賽秘境的靈魂。

==劇情==
阿寶同意幫艾薇爾錄製她的音樂作品後，她開始唱一首〈The Fry Song〉，關於她和她父親亨森·阿巴迪爾之間的裂痕。阿寶感到遺憾，故決定召喚從地獄般的惡夜魔境，她的父親，但不知道父親是黑暗區域的首領，而且會吸收靈魂。他在艾薇爾和阿寶面前出現，並意圖殺阿寶及成功地搶走艾薇爾的斧頭貝斯。於是阿寶和艾薇爾追他。

艾薇爾的父親漂流在哇賽秘境吸收自己能找到所有活生物的靈魂。阿寶和艾薇爾一開始想用岩石打他，但是只會激怒亨森·阿巴迪爾所造成父親和女兒之間的衝突。阿寶預設艾薇爾殺死他後接管惡夜魔境，但她只想拿回低音吉他。

就在阿寶和艾薇爾最後一次阻止亨森·阿巴迪爾，他現在變得巨大。由於體型，阿寶很容易被打敗。艾薇爾因父親的不理解而氣沖沖地離去。阿寶用最後一搏，播放〈The Fry Song〉的錄音。忽然，艾薇爾的父親明白她為什麼生氣，兩個重新連繫。阿寶擊掌，找到機會從亨森·阿巴迪爾的“靈魂袋”切開，放出所有的靈魂，並把他趕回惡夜魔境。

==幕後製作==
[[File:Ukulele1_HiRes.jpg|這集由分鏡美術設計{{le]]的〈The Fry Song〉於電視台播出。|thumb|left|150px]]
《惡夜魔境》是由{{le|亞當·武藤|Adam Muto}}和{{le|雷貝卡·素格|Rebecca Sugar}}分別擔任編劇及分鏡，{{le|梅里韋瑟·威廉|Merriwether Williams}}、小史蒂夫、{{le|派屈克·麥克海爾|Patrick McHale(cartoonist)}}、[[潘得頓·沃德|潘得頓·沃德]]和{{le|色普·范·奧爾曼|Thurop Van Orman}}擔任故事構成<ref name=episodecredits/>。此集是{{le|雷貝卡·素格|Rebecca Sugar}}第一次擔任分鏡；據她所說，她“做了所有怪物的東西在結尾部分”，而武藤“做了所有的肉於中途部分”<ref name=firstboard/>。後來玩笑說“真正機智的東西是亞當做的。通常我負責性笑話和暴力”<ref name=firstboard/>。製作分鏡的過程中，素格和武藤所需時間不夠，因此，武藤請藝術家同事{{le|傑西·莫伊尼漢|Jesse Moynihan}}如果他能幫助艾薇爾和父親之間的開戰之分鏡<ref name=muto>Muto, Adam (Storyboard artist). 2013. "It Came from the Nightosphere" [Commentary track], ''Adventure Time'' Season Two [DVD], Los Angeles, CA: [[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]].</ref><ref name=jesse>Moynihan, Jesse (Storyboard artist). 2013. "It Came from the Nightosphere" [Commentary track], ''Adventure Time'' Season Two [DVD], Los Angeles, CA: [[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]].</ref>。最後一橋段是阿巴迪爾被阿寶切開他的“靈魂袋”是出自沃德的圖畫中阿寶配著兩把劍在空中飛，素格增加之<ref name=sugar/><ref name=ward>Ward, Pendleton (Series creator). 2013. "It Came from the Nightosphere" [Commentary track], ''Adventure Time'' Season Two [DVD], Los Angeles, CA: [[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]].</ref>。然而，她不確定該橋段是否會成為最終成果，由於圖形性質<ref name=sugar>Sugar, Rebecca (Storyboard artist). 2013. "It Came from the Nightosphere" [Commentary track], ''Adventure Time'' Season Two [DVD], Los Angeles, CA: [[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]].</ref>。艾薇爾爸爸遇到阿鵝的橋段啟發編劇寫[[探險活寶_(第四季)|第四季]]《阿鵝新王國》<ref name=kent>Osborne, Kent (Storyboard artist). 2013. "It Came from the Nightosphere" [Commentary track], ''Adventure Time'' Season Two [DVD], Los Angeles, CA: [[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]].</ref>。

〈The Fry Song〉是沃德和素格共同作詞。<ref name=sugar/><ref name=music>Ward, Pendleton, et al. 2014. "Distant Bands: The Music of Adventure Time" [Featurette], ''Adventure Time'' Season Four [DVD], Los Angeles, CA: [[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]].</ref>這是她寫的第一首歌，受《探險活寶》的影迷歡迎。<ref name=sugar/><ref>{{cite web|title=A Kettle of 'Fry Songs'|url=http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/12/13/a-kettle-of-fry-songs/|publisher=[[Frederator|Frederator]]|accessdate=June 4, 2013|date=December 13, 2010|archive-date=2013-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130522084245/http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/12/13/a-kettle-of-fry-songs/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>素格的原始版靈感來自[[百老匯戲劇|百老匯戲劇]]，且風格陰沉。沃德協助素格添加更多笑話至最終版本<ref name=music/>。沃德擔任[[節奏口技|節奏口技]]和素格彈[[烏克麗麗|烏克麗麗]]，兩人表演〈The Fry Song〉。素格後來說是“超可怕”的體驗，但電視台[[綠燈_(電影製作)|正式同意核准]]<ref name=firstboard>{{cite web|last=Seibert|first=Fred|title=Rebecca Sugar’s First Board (Nightosphere)|url=http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/10/11/rebecca-sugars-first-board-nightosphere/|publisher=[[Frederator_Studios|Frederator Studios]]|accessdate=January 19, 2013|date=October 11, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130828054918/http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/10/11/rebecca-sugars-first-board-nightosphere|archive-date=2013-08-28|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。此集是本季製作的第三集，但被決定第一集播出。電視台宣布第二季開始時還沒有完成。執行製作人{{le|弗雷德·塞伯特|Fred Seibert}}在他的個人網站上指出，他“寧可跳至第二季之前的幾集，但不是我那電視台<ref name=seibertsite>{{cite web|last=Seibert|first=Fred|title=Season Two Premieres Next Monday…|url=http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/10/04/season-two-premieres-next-monday/|publisher=[[Frederator_Studios|Frederator Studios]]|accessdate=January 19, 2013|date=October 4, 2010|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422015450/http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/10/04/season-two-premieres-next-monday/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。塞伯特還認為此集相當可怕，並警告觀看者可能不適合年幼兒童<ref name=seibertsite/>。

配演艾薇爾的奧利維亞·奧森的父親{{le|馬丁·奧森|Martin Olson}}，則配演艾薇爾的惡魔父親亨森·阿巴迪爾<ref>{{cite web|title=Martin Olson|url=http://www.behindthevoiceactors.com/Martin-Olson/|publisher=Behind the Voice Actors|accessdate=March 18, 2013|archive-date=2012-10-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121008000341/http://www.behindthevoiceactors.com/Martin-Olson/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=rocketmag/><ref>{{cite web|last=Seibert|first=Fred|title='Nightosphere' Odds and Ends|url=http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/10/12/nightosphere-odds-ends/|publisher=[[Frederator|Frederator]]|accessdate=March 18, 2013|date=October 12, 2010|archive-date=2012-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120722212637/http://archives.frederatorblogs.com/adventure_time/2010/10/12/nightosphere-odds-ends/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。選派角色之後的一年，沃德找奧森商量，問他是否想配演節目角色。奧森起初很擔心，認為他不是演員，而是作家。沃德仍然堅持，奧森最終答應。奧森後來開玩笑說他在錄對話錄音時“處在天堂”，因為此集是他“與[他的]女兒戰鬥至死。”<ref name=soundcloudoliviamartin>{{cite web|last=Smith|first=Zack|title=Adventure Time Ancient Psychic Tandem Warcast Episode 5|url=https://soundcloud.com/zack-smith-81/martin-and-olivia-final|publisher=[[Soundcloud|Soundcloud]]|accessdate=May 3, 2014|date=April 14, 2014|archive-date=2014-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140503090827/https://soundcloud.com/zack-smith-81/martin-and-olivia-final|dead-url=no}}</ref>奧利維亞後來指出，與父親互動配音的機會“很酷”<ref name=rocketmag>{{cite web|last=Gaddy|first=Laura|title=Comic-Con Interview with Adventure Time!|url=http://racketmag.com/interviews/comic-con-interview-with-adventure-time/|work=Rocket Magazine|accessdate=March 18, 2013|date=July 28, 2011|archive-date=2012-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120814212709/http://racketmag.com/interviews/comic-con-interview-with-adventure-time/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。奧森將在[[探險活寶_(第三季)|第三季]]《記憶的記憶》客串，並將在第四季《重返惡夜魔境/爸爸的小怪物》當主要角色<ref>{{cite episode| title=Memory of a Memory| series=Adventure Time| serieslink=|credits = Larry Leichliter (director); Tom Herpich & Ako Castuera (writers) | network = [[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]] |airdate=July 25, 2011 | season = 3 | number = 3}}</ref><ref name="They Went To The Nightosphere/Daddy’s Little Monster">{{cite web|url=http://www.avclub.com/articles/they-went-to-the-nightosphere-pt-1daddys-little-mo,72851/|title='They Went To The Nightosphere'/'Daddy’s Little Monster' {{!}} Adventure Time {{!}} TV Club|date=April 30, 2012|publisher=[[The_Onion|The Onion]]|work=[[The_A.V._Club|The A.V. Club]]|author=Dyess-Nugent, Phil|accessdate=August 22, 2012|archive-date=2013-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921141345/http://www.avclub.com/articles/they-went-to-the-nightosphere-pt-1daddys-little-mo,72851/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿巴迪爾的怪物設計引起[[廣播標準和規範_(美國)|標準和規範]]部門的問題。最初設計被認為“太像[[陰道|陰道]]”，電視台叫節目重新設計過角色<ref name=austin/>。然而，在第二次提交時，電視台認為看起來“太像[[陰莖|陰莖]]”<ref name=austin/>。沃德後來說，“我們就像，‘發生了什麼？這是一個怪物，只是有張一個瘋狂、奇怪的臉。’”<ref name=austin>{{cite web|last=Sanders|first=Austin|title=Talking to the Minds Behind Adventure Time: Pendleton Ward and Tom Kenny|url=http://austin.culturemap.com/news/music_film/05-01-12-15-00-talking-to-the-minds-behind-adventure-time/|publisher=CultureMap Austin|accessdate=June 6, 2013|date=May 1, 2012|archive-date=2013-06-15|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615202013/http://austin.culturemap.com/news/music_film/05-01-12-15-00-talking-to-the-minds-behind-adventure-time/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《惡夜魔境》沒有公開阿巴迪爾的名字，只是提到是“艾薇爾的爸爸”。直到第四季之前，他的全名不會公開<ref name=episodecredits>{{cite episode| title=It Came from the Nightosphere| series=Adventure Time| serieslink=|credits = Larry Leichliter (director); Adam Muto & [[Rebecca_Sugar|Rebecca Sugar]] (writers) | network = [[Cartoon_Network|Cartoon Network]] |airdate=October 11, 2010 | season = 2 | number = 1}}</ref><ref name="They Went To The Nightosphere/Daddy’s Little Monster"/>。根據莫伊尼漢，這個名字是源自他的兄弟在成長階段時給他們的家人的車名。兩人後來當做樂團，只錄製一首歌<ref name=jesse/>。

==反響==
《惡夜魔境》於2010年10月11日在卡通頻道首播。此集有200.1萬觀眾觀看，[[尼爾森收視率|尼爾森收視率]]為1.3/2，表示所有家庭在看電視時的比例為1.3%和2%<ref name=nightratings>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/10/12/monday-cable-ratings-monday-night-football-up-%E2%80%98real-housewives-of-atlanta%E2%80%99-american-pickers-slip-mlb-playoffs-more/67795|title=Monday Cable Ratings: Monday Night Football Up; ‘Real Housewives of Atlanta,’ ‘American Pickers’ Slip, MLB Playoffs & More|last=Gorman|first=Bill|work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|publisher=[[Zap2it|Zap2it]]|date=October 12, 2010|accessdate=October 12, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101125113655/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/10/12/monday-cable-ratings-monday-night-football-up-%E2%80%98real-housewives-of-atlanta%E2%80%99-american-pickers-slip-mlb-playoffs-more/67795|archivedate=2010年11月25日}}</ref>。表示與第一季首集相比下降，有250萬觀眾，但與第一季結局相比，只有增加177萬觀眾觀看<ref name=firstep>{{cite web|url=http://tvbythenumbers.com/2010/04/06/monday-cable-pawning-damages-em-nurse-jackie-damaged/47625|title=Monday Cable: Pawning & Picking Good for History; "Damages " & "Nurse Jackie" Damaged|first=Robert|last=Seidman|date=April 6, 2010|accessdate=April 24, 2010|work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|publisher=[[Zap2it|Zap2it]]|archive-date=2013-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104081332/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/04/06/monday-cable-pawning-damages-em-nurse-jackie-damaged/47625/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=finale1>{{cite web|title=Monday's Cable Ratings: 'MNF' a Ratings Juggernaut|url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/ratings/2010/09/28/mondays-cable-ratings-mnf-a-ratings-juggernaut-37654/cable_20100927/|publisher=The Futon Critic|accessdate=January 11, 2013|date=September 28, 2010}}</ref>。《惡夜魔境》也與一年前的同時間段相比顯著增加；例如，有732萬6-11歲兒童觀看，與前年相比增加35%。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gorman|first=Bill|title=Ratings Notes for TBS, TNT, Cartoon Network, Adult Swim and truTV; Including MLB Division Series Averages|url=http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/10/12/ratings-notes-for-tbs-tnt-cartoon-network-adult-swim-and-trutv-including-mlb-division-series-averages/67703/|work=[[TV_by_the_Numbers|TV by the Numbers]]|publisher=[[Zap2it|Zap2it]]|accessdate=January 19, 2013|date=October 12, 2010|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205855/http://tvbythenumbers.zap2it.com/2010/10/12/ratings-notes-for-tbs-tnt-cartoon-network-adult-swim-and-trutv-including-mlb-division-series-averages/67703/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>此集首次在2012年《惡夜魔境》的DVD發行，其中包括前三季的16集<ref>{{cite video  | people = Larry Leichliter, et al. | year = 2012 | title = Adventure Time: It Came From the Nightosphere | medium = DVD | publisher = [[Warner_Home_Video|Warner Home Video]] }}</ref>後來在2013年6月完整版第二季DVD發行<ref>{{cite video  | people = Larry Leichliter, et al. | year = 2013 | title = Adventure Time: The Complete Second  Season | medium = DVD | publisher = [[Warner_Home_Video|Warner Home Video]]}}</ref>。

《惡夜魔境》被評論者接受極佳。[[網路品牌|DVD Talk]]的泰勒·福斯特（Tyler Foster）說“這個節目可以擊敗所有記錄的像樣例子”<ref name=dvdtalk>{{cite web|last=Foster|first=Tyler|title=Adventure Time: It Came From the Nightosphere|url=http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/53920/adventure-time-it-came-from-the-nightosphere/|work=[[DVD_Talk|DVD Talk]]|publisher=[[Internet_Brands|Internet Brands]]|accessdate=February 6, 2013|date=March 6, 2012|archive-date=2014-08-02|archive-url=https://archive.today/20140802104833/http://www.dvdtalk.com/reviews/53920/adventure-time-it-came-from-the-nightosphere/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他特別對“艾薇爾和她爸爸之間處理嚴肅的裂痕，適合在企鵝附近的荒謬噱頭”的方式感到高興<ref name=dvdtalk/>。他還指出，“任何劇集包括一首歌曲在我的歌詞裡都有加分”<ref name=dvdtalk/>。被稱為[[MTV|MTV Geek]]查爾斯·韋伯（Charles Webb）發行同名DVD的“真正的亮點”<ref>{{cite web|last=Webb|first=Charles|title=DVD Review: 'Adventure Time: It Came From the Nightosphere'|url=http://geek-news.mtv.com/2012/03/08/dvd-review-adventure-time-it-came-from-the-nightosphere/|work=MTV Geek|publisher=[[MTV|MTV]]|accessdate=February 6, 2013|date=March 18, 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120911010044/http://geek-news.mtv.com/2012/03/08/dvd-review-adventure-time-it-came-from-the-nightosphere/|archivedate=2012年9月11日}}</ref>。[[IGN|IGN]]作家馬特·福勒（Matt Fowler）後來論此集“經典”<ref name=ign1>{{cite web|last=Fowler|first=Matt|title=Adventure Time Creator: It's Awesome If We Give People Nightmares|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/03/05/adventure-time-creator-its-awesome-if-we-give-people-nightmares|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[News_Corporation|News Corporation]]|accessdate=May 31, 2013|date=March 5, 2012|archive-date=2016-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161204073610/http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/03/05/adventure-time-creator-its-awesome-if-we-give-people-nightmares|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在單一評論，他後來寫道此集“已代表《探險活寶》中最好，譬如艾薇爾的反爸爸歌就是這樣，且她的{{le|弗雷迪·克魯格|Freddy Krueger}}式毛衣已推出一千件[[cosplay|cosplay]]”<ref name=ignreviewseason2>{{cite web|last=Fowler|first=Matt|title=Adventure Time: The Complete Second Season|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/27/adventure-time-the-complete-second-season-blu-ray-review|work=[[IGN|IGN]]|publisher=[[News_Corporation|News Corporation]]|accessdate=July 1, 2013|date=June 27, 2013|archive-date=2013-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130630131907/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/06/27/adventure-time-the-complete-second-season-blu-ray-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

沃德對集此感到非常高興。他稱讚分鏡設計武藤和素格，說前者“有個令人捧腹的鬧劇點睛之筆設置的喜劇風格”，後者“執行這些超級浪漫、情感雞皮疙瘩的感覺是令人驚奇的。<ref name=ign1/>他對結局特別高興，指出“我喜歡這種在音樂增強而高潮的場景，有雞皮疙瘩的感覺。在那集你正在談論有向上的情節至結束，然後腫泡泡公主[...]在中間切入並說‘戲劇炸彈！’，類似像切腿，這是我認為有很多有趣的地方。”<ref>{{cite news|last=Guzman|first=René|title=Quirky, Fun 'Adventure Time' Delves Into the Dark Side Too|url=http://docs.newsbank.com.www2.lib.ku.edu:2048/s/InfoWeb/aggdocs/NewsBank/13D5944373256240/0F8479522BD09CA1?s_lang=en-US|newspaper=[[San_Antonio_Express-News|San Antonio Express-News]]|publisher=[[Hearst_Corporation|Hearst Corporation]]|accessdate=February 6, 2013|date=March 6, 2012}} {{subscription required}}</ref>此集後來被提名為2011年[[黃金時段艾美獎|黃金時段艾美獎]]傑出短篇動畫節目，但沒獲獎<ref>{{cite web|title=Outstanding Short-Form Animated Program 2011|url=http://www.emmys.com/nominations/2011/Outstanding%20Short-format%20Animated%20Program|work=''Emmys.com''|publisher=[[Academy_of_Television_Arts_&_Sciences|Academy of Television Arts & Sciences]]|accessdate=January 19, 2013|archive-date=2013-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722183422/http://www.emmys.com/nominations/2011/Outstanding|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

